generic:link.msg:message: (Total of significant counterparty - deposits (domestic)) = "Sum of all counterparty".
(Total of significant counterparty - deposits (overseas)) = "Sum of all counterparty".
(Total of significant counterparty - borrowings (domestic)) = "Sum of all significant counterparty".
(Total of significant counterparty - borrowings (overseas)) = "Sum of all significant counterparty".
"Total Deposits of Top 20 Large Deposits (domestic) related to specific depositor" = (Savings Deposits + Current Deposits + Term Deposits)
"Total Deposits of Top 20 Large Deposits (overseas) related to specific depositor" = (Savings Deposits + Current Deposits + Term Deposits)
"Total Deposits of Top 20 Large Deposits (domestic)" should be equal to "sum of total of each top twenty large depositors".
"Total Deposits of Top 20 Large Deposits (overseas)" should be equal to "sum of total of each top twenty large depositors".
"Total borrowings (domestic)" should be equal to sum of "Total of top 10 borrowings".
"Total borrowings (overseas)" should be equal to sum of "Total of top 10 borrowings".
"Total liabilities from Significant instrument/product (domestic)" = "Sum of all significant instrument/product".
"Total liabilities from Significant instrument/product (overseas)" = "Sum of all significant instrument/product".
"Total Liabilities from funding sources through Securitisation (domestic)" should be equal to "sum of all funding sources through Securitisation".
"Total Liabilities from funding sources through Securitisation (overseas)" should be equal to "sum of all funding sources through Securitisation".
"Percentage of total deposits of significant counterparty (domestic)" = (bank deposits of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Deposits).
"Percentage of total deposits of significant counterparty (overseas)" = (bank deposits of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Deposits).
"Percentage of liabilities of significant counterparty (domestic)" = (bank deposits of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities).
"Percentage of liabilities of significant counterparty (overseas)" = (bank deposits of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities).
"Percentage of borrowings of significant counterparty (domestic)" = (bank borrowings of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Borrowings).
"Percentage of borrowings of significant counterparty (overseas)" = (bank borrowings of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Borrowings).
"Percentage of liabilities of significant counterparty (domestic)" = (bank borrowings of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities).
"Percentage of liabilities of significant counterparty (overseas)" = (bank borrowings of significant counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities).
"Percentage of total deposits of Top 20 Large counterparty (domestic)" = (bank deposits of Top 20 Large counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Deposits).
"Percentage of total deposits of Top 20 Large counterparty (overseas)" = (bank deposits of Top 20 Large counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Deposits).
"Percentage of total borrowings of Top 10 counterparty (domestic)" = (bank borrowings of Top 10 counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Borrowings).
"Percentage of total borrowings of Top 10 counterparty (overseas)" = (bank borrowings of Top 10 counterparty multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Borrowings).
"Percentage of total liabilities from Significant instrument/product (domestic)" = (bank liabilities of Significant instrument/product multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities).
"Percentage of total liabilities from Significant instrument/product (overseas)" = (bank liabilities of Significant instrument/product multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities).

"Percentage of total liabilities from funding sources through Securitisation (domestic)" = "bank liabilities of funding sources through Securitisation multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities".

"Percentage of total liabilities from funding sources through Securitisation (overseas)" = "bank liabilities of funding sources through Securitisation multiplied by 100 and divided by Bank's Total Liabilities".
"Bank's Total Deposits (Domestic)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Liabilities (Domestic)".
"Bank's Total Deposits (Overseas)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Liabilities (Overseas)".
"Bank's Total Borrowings (Domestic)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Liabilities (Domestic)".
"Bank's Total Borrowings (Overseas)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Liabilities (Overseas)".
(Total of Significant Counterparty - Deposits (Domestic)) should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Deposit (Domestic)".
(Total of Significant Counterparty - Deposits (Overseas)) should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Deposit (Overseas)".
(Total of Significant Counterparty - Borrowings (Domestic)) should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Borrowings (Domestic)".
(Total of Significant Counterparty - Borrowings (Overseas)) should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Borrowings (Overseas)".
"Total of Top 20 Depositors (Domestic)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Deposits (Domestic)".
"Total of Top 20 Depositors (Overseas)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Deposits (Overseas)".
"Total of Top 10 Borrowing (Domestic)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Borrowings (Domestic)".
"Total of Top 10 Borrowing (Overseas)" should be less than or equal to "Bank's Total Borrowings (Overseas)".
Value should be in positive.
Value should be in positive.
"Bank's Total Liabilities (Domestic)" should be more than or equal to (Bank's Total Deposits (Domestic) + Bank's Total Borrowings (Domestic)).
"Bank's Total Liabilities (Overseas)" should be more than or equal to (Bank's Total Deposits (Overseas) + Bank's Total Borrowings (Overseas)).
"Bank's Total Deposit in domestic sheet" should be same as "Bank's Total Deposit in Overseas sheet".
"Bank's Total Borrowings in domestic sheet" should be same as "Bank's Total Borrowings in Overseas sheet".
"Bank's Total Liabilities in domestic sheet" should be same as "Bank's Total Liabilities in Overseas sheet".
